@page "/about"


<MudContainer>
    <MudPaper Elevation="1" Class="pa-6">
        <MudText Variant="h4" GutterBottom Class="mb-4">
            <b>About SailView</b>
        </MudText>
        <MudText Paragraph Class="mb-4">
            Welcome to SailView, the ultimate sailing race results processing and visualisation platform. Designed for sailing enthusiasts, race organizers, and competitors alike, SailView streamlines the race data management process and brings the excitement of sailing to life through stunning visualisations.
        </MudText>
        <MudText Paragraph Class="mb-4">
            SailView is dedicated to helping you quickly and accurately process race results while also providing comprehensive analytics and visual representations. With SailView, you can easily manage multiple race series, track competitor performance, and explore race statistics in a user-friendly format.
        </MudText>
        <MudText Variant="h5" GutterBottom Class="mb-4">
            How to Use SailView:
        </MudText>
        <MudList>        
                <MudListItem Text="1. Register or Login: If you are a new user, register for an account to get started. If you already have an account, simply log in to access your dashboard." />
                <MudListItem Text="2. Create a Race Series: Begin by creating a new race series. Input the series name and select the races you want to include. You can create multiple race series based on different events or categories."/>
                <MudListItem Text="3. Enter Race Data: Input race results for each race in the series. You can add, edit, or delete race data at any time. SailView supports various scoring systems and automatically calculates overall scores, rankings, and tiebreakers." />
                <MudListItem Text="4. Visualise Race Results: Explore the interactive visualisations to gain insights into race performance and trends. Analyze competitor standings, race progress, and overall statistics. Share these visualisations with others or embed them on your website to keep everyone informed." />
                <MudListItem Text="5. Manage Competitors: Keep track of all competitors and their information. Easily update competitor details, assign them to races, and view their performance across different race series." />
        </MudList>
        <MudText Paragraph>
            With SailView, sailing race management and analysis have never been easier or more engaging. Transform the way you process race results, gain insights into performance, and share the excitement of sailing with others. SailView is your one-stop solution for efficient and comprehensive sailing race result management.
        </MudText>
    </MudPaper>
</MudContainer>



